          "description": "Great pharmacy. I get all my prescriptions filled here. There\u2019s never a long line, and no one rushes you. Much prefer it over any of the big chains. Just as affordable. - four year update; it\u2019s still my pharmacy. They go the extra mile! And they are well stocked in terms of convincence items as well . \ud83d\ude4c\ud83c\udffd\ud83e\udd70",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNVZ296MFJnEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x10d3356546e7aeab!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICUgoz0Rg%7C%7C?hl=en",
