          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFyQN-1C8SkZyCBQUCYLe610TXiYNOJ1rHoEFmKY62JgdCmRgY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I love this place for many reasons! Firstly, they are the nicest pharmacist ever. They help with all questions and make you feel welcome. I feel like I have known them forever when it's only been a couple of months. If they don't have the medicine they will order it for you. If they are closed, they have a drop off box so they can have it ready for you first thing in the morning. It also has that local business charm that many places like Duane Reade and Rite Aid don't have.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUN3dlppNkdBEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x10d3356546e7aeab!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICwvZi6GA%7C%7C?hl=en",
